that attracted all the wandering ghosts
and the lost spirits of beasts…

790
01:14:48,750 --> 01:14:54,166
such as snakes, dogs, centipedes, spiders…

791
01:14:55,541 --> 01:14:57,458
and those of plants and grasses.

792
01:14:59,625 --> 01:15:05,041
They've gathered together
and become a very powerful, evil demon.

793
01:15:12,291 --> 01:15:13,250
Right here.

794
01:15:13,791 --> 01:15:14,833
This is where I found Mink.

795
01:15:18,750 --> 01:15:20,375
We'll conduct the ceremony right here,

796
01:15:22,416 --> 01:15:24,208
where all the evil spirits
originated from.

797
01:15:25,208 --> 01:15:29,500
If we can get rid of them,
their slivers in Mink will also disappear.

798
01:15:30,500 --> 01:15:32,250
And why does it have to be Mink?

799
01:15:33,625 --> 01:15:38,125
Do you know about the ancestors
of your husband's family?

800
01:15:41,000 --> 01:15:45,416
Wiroj's ancestors
beheaded thousands of people.

801
01:15:47,750 --> 01:15:51,875
The last wishes of those dying people
were to curse the family,

802
01:15:53,333 --> 01:15:56,916
and their offspring
never stopped making bad karma.

803
01:15:59,208 --> 01:16:00,208
And Wiroj…

804
01:16:01,208 --> 01:16:02,458
married you.

805
01:16:04,375 --> 01:16:05,708
The one who rejected Ba Yan.

806
01:16:14,666 --> 01:16:15,791
From then on…

807
01:16:18,208 --> 01:16:20,041
everything was destined to be that

808
01:16:22,125 --> 01:16:25,000
the one who has to pay redemption is Mink.

809
01:16:38,000 --> 01:16:39,791
Do you think it's reasonable?

810
01:16:42,375 --> 01:16:45,000
About what Santi said,
that everything was destined.

811
01:16:47,291 --> 01:16:50,583
Don't worry.
We'll get the auspicious date soon.

812
01:16:50,666 --> 01:16:52,208
Destined by who?

813
01:16:54,041 --> 01:16:55,000
By God?

814
01:16:55,875 --> 01:16:57,375
By Buddha?

815
01:16:57,458 --> 01:16:59,250
Or by other deities?

816
01:17:02,041 --> 01:17:05,041
If it's the ancestors
that created bad karma,

817
01:17:05,125 --> 01:17:09,166
why does Mink have to pay for it?
Why not me?

818
01:17:17,375 --> 01:17:18,333
Go sit over there first.

819
01:17:22,166 --> 01:17:23,791
You don't have to think too much.

820
01:17:25,375 --> 01:17:27,708
Once the ceremony is done,
Mink will get better.

821
01:17:28,416 --> 01:17:29,916
Ba Yan will help us.

822
01:17:32,500 --> 01:17:34,083
Back then, when I was sick,

823
01:17:35,041 --> 01:17:37,666
everyone said
Ba Yan was going to possess me.

824
01:17:38,708 --> 01:17:40,666
But I didn't feel anything.

825
01:17:41,375 --> 01:17:42,958
I was just sick.

826
01:17:46,291 --> 01:17:47,583
Let me ask you something.

827
01:17:49,916 --> 01:17:51,708
Have you ever seen Ba Yan?

828
01:17:53,791 --> 01:17:55,458
Is there really a Ba Yan?

829
01:17:57,000 --> 01:17:58,208
Of course, there is.

830
01:17:59,541 --> 01:18:00,875
Have you ever seen Her?

831
01:18:04,291 --> 01:18:05,166
No.

832
01:18:07,458 --> 01:18:09,166
Then how do you know?

833
01:18:10,666 --> 01:18:11,791
I can feel it.

834
01:18:16,333 --> 01:18:17,500
I can feel Her.

835
01:18:25,083 --> 01:18:27,000
You have to believe in Ba Yan,

836
01:18:28,083 --> 01:18:29,375
and She will help us.

837
01:18:48,458 --> 01:18:49,750
To perform this ceremony,

838
01:18:49,833 --> 01:18:52,291
the more evil and dangerous
the spirits are,

839
01:18:52,375 --> 01:18:53,833
the more I have to be prepared.

840
01:18:54,791 --> 01:18:58,541
I have to make lots of talismans
and consecrate them all,

841
01:18:58,625 --> 01:19:00,750
including a sacred wand.

842
01:19:05,041 --> 01:19:07,416
I consecrate them over and over
with all the power I have.

843
01:19:11,166 --> 01:19:14,041
And I also have to prepare holy water,
candles, and incense.

844
01:19:14,125 --> 01:19:15,583
It's really an extravagant affair.

845
01:19:16,666 --> 01:19:19,583
Most importantly,
I have to do the ceremony with Nim.

846
01:19:20,708 --> 01:19:22,458
Nim and I have to be united as one.

847
01:19:23,041 --> 01:19:25,583
It's really tough, but it's challenging.

848
01:19:26,083 --> 01:19:28,250
Although, I've been doing this
for a long time.

849
01:19:28,333 --> 01:19:29,791
Let's see how tough they are.

850
01:19:38,000 --> 01:19:40,166
She won't eat anything.

851
01:19:40,750 --> 01:19:43,291
When I talk with her, she's not receptive.

852
01:19:45,333 --> 01:19:46,916
I'm really stressed out.

853
01:19:49,625 --> 01:19:52,041
Nim hasn't come either. She's been busy

854
01:19:52,125 --> 01:19:54,708
with the ceremony preparations.

855
01:19:54,791 --> 01:19:56,666
One other thing…

856
01:19:57,291 --> 01:20:01,250
every morning when I come down,
the house is a total mess.

857
01:20:03,458 --> 01:20:06,666
It must be Mink. She does it every night.

858
01:20:06,750 --> 01:20:08,166
I don't know what she does.

859
01:20:10,916 --> 01:20:13,833
THE TEAM DECIDES TO INSTALL CAMERAS
INSIDE THE HOUSE

860
01:20:14,375 --> 01:20:17,625
TO OBSERVE MINK'S BEHAVIOR AT NIGHT.

