876
01:24:07,583 --> 01:24:09,291
I'm staying here with my child.

877
01:24:12,166 --> 01:24:13,375
I admit that…

878
01:24:14,333 --> 01:24:15,833
it looks scary.

879
01:24:17,958 --> 01:24:19,833
But she's still my child.

880
01:24:22,083 --> 01:24:24,333
It won't be long until she gets better.

881
01:24:25,583 --> 01:24:27,083
Nim will help her.

882
01:24:28,791 --> 01:24:31,958
Nim is an expert.
She's helped lots of people.

883
01:24:32,041 --> 01:24:33,416
She can definitely help Mink.

884
01:24:34,208 --> 01:24:35,041
Don't you think?

885
01:24:40,333 --> 01:24:43,458
AFTER SEEING MINK'S BEHAVIOR,

886
01:24:43,541 --> 01:24:48,875
THE FAMILY MEMBERS ALLOWED THE TEAM
TO INSTALL MORE CAMERAS.

887
01:26:08,041 --> 01:26:09,041
What's wrong?

888
01:26:09,791 --> 01:26:10,833
My stomach hurts.

889
01:26:27,333 --> 01:26:29,583
2 DAYS BEFORE THE CEREMONY

890
01:26:33,666 --> 01:26:34,583
Done.

891
01:26:35,250 --> 01:26:36,666
