899
01:28:39,708 --> 01:28:40,541
Pong!

900
01:28:43,750 --> 01:28:45,416
Pong! Mink!

901
01:28:45,500 --> 01:28:46,333
Mink!

902
01:28:47,291 --> 01:28:48,208
Mink!

903
01:28:54,541 --> 01:28:55,375
Pang!

904
01:28:56,208 --> 01:28:57,041
Pang!

905
01:28:58,666 --> 01:28:59,541
Pong!

