912
01:29:09,791 --> 01:29:12,625
-She took my son.
-Where did she take Pong?

913
01:29:12,708 --> 01:29:13,541
Mink.

914
01:29:14,208 --> 01:29:16,000
Let's go find him.

915
01:29:17,208 --> 01:29:18,208
Pong!

916
01:29:19,333 --> 01:29:20,916
Where did she take him?

917
01:29:21,625 --> 01:29:23,416
Come on. Let's go search.

918
01:29:23,500 --> 01:29:25,083
Mink!

919
01:29:25,166 --> 01:29:27,208
Why did you take my kid?

920
01:29:27,291 --> 01:29:28,750
Have you lost it?

921
01:29:28,833 --> 01:29:29,708
Mink.

922
01:29:30,625 --> 01:29:31,500
Mink.

923
01:29:32,708 --> 01:29:33,583
Mink!

924
01:29:35,916 --> 01:29:36,791
Mink!

925
01:29:36,875 --> 01:29:37,958
Have you seen Mink?

926
01:29:38,041 --> 01:29:39,375
No.

927
01:29:39,458 --> 01:29:40,333
Mink!

928
01:29:42,833 --> 01:29:43,916
Mink!

929
01:29:45,250 --> 01:29:46,375
Mink!

930
01:29:47,958 --> 01:29:51,208
Damn it! Why are you doing this?

931
01:29:51,291 --> 01:29:54,333
Mink! Where are you?

932
01:29:54,416 --> 01:29:55,375
Mink!

933
01:30:01,083 --> 01:30:01,916
Pong.

934
01:30:05,291 --> 01:30:06,166
Pong!

935
01:30:07,333 --> 01:30:08,166
Pong!

936
01:30:11,166 --> 01:30:12,208
Pong!

937
01:30:13,000 --> 01:30:13,916
My boy.

938
01:30:21,750 --> 01:30:22,750
Pong!

939
01:30:23,625 --> 01:30:24,750
Pong!

940
01:30:34,833 --> 01:30:36,416
It's all right now, baby.

941
01:30:39,166 --> 01:30:40,000
Mink?

942
01:30:41,583 --> 01:30:42,416
Mink!

943
01:30:44,375 --> 01:30:45,208
Mink!

944
01:30:45,708 --> 01:30:46,666
Mink!

945
01:30:47,791 --> 01:30:48,625
Mink!

946
01:30:53,041 --> 01:30:53,875
Mink!

947
01:31:32,083 --> 01:31:32,958
Mink.

948
01:31:42,708 --> 01:31:43,541
Mink!

949
01:31:43,625 --> 01:31:44,583
What the hell?

950
01:31:47,916 --> 01:31:48,750
Mink!

951
01:31:49,375 --> 01:31:50,291
Mink.

952
01:31:50,375 --> 01:31:51,375
Let go of him.

953
01:32:01,791 --> 01:32:06,541
1 DAY BEFORE THE CEREMONY

954
01:32:13,666 --> 01:32:14,583
Nim.

955
01:32:18,250 --> 01:32:19,583
Is something wrong?

956
01:32:20,958 --> 01:32:23,875
I've been calling her since last night,
but she hasn't answered.

957
01:32:24,416 --> 01:32:27,291
I can hear her phone ringing.
Why won't she answer it?

958
01:32:28,041 --> 01:32:30,125
I'll go get help.

959
01:32:30,208 --> 01:32:31,291
Okay.

960
01:32:35,541 --> 01:32:36,375
Nim.

961
01:32:37,375 --> 01:32:38,208
Nim.

962
01:32:39,625 --> 01:32:40,875
Nim!

963
01:32:40,958 --> 01:32:42,291
Where are you?

964
01:32:43,416 --> 01:32:44,291
Nim.

965
01:32:55,375 --> 01:32:56,916
Why are there so many maggots?

966
01:32:59,000 --> 01:32:59,833
Nim.

967
01:33:00,416 --> 01:33:01,291
Nim.

968
01:33:03,750 --> 01:33:04,583
Nim!

969
01:33:05,208 --> 01:33:06,041
Nim!

970
01:33:06,583 --> 01:33:08,125
Nim! Wake up.

971
01:33:08,208 --> 01:33:09,708
Why are you sleeping like this?

972
01:33:10,416 --> 01:33:11,291
Nim!

973
01:33:11,833 --> 01:33:13,541
Nim!

974
01:33:13,625 --> 01:33:15,500
Hurry, come help me!

975
01:33:15,583 --> 01:33:17,541
I don't know what's with her! Nim!

976
01:33:18,083 --> 01:33:20,333
NIM DIED WHILE ASLEEP.

977
01:33:20,416 --> 01:33:26,666
ISAN PEOPLE CALL IT "LAI TAI."

978
01:33:28,083 --> 01:33:32,583
DOCTORS COULD NOT CONCLUDE
THE CAUSE OF DEATH.

979
01:33:39,416 --> 01:33:41,541
Nim died because of me.

980
01:33:43,958 --> 01:33:46,583
Mink is like this because of me.

981
01:33:48,041 --> 01:33:49,875
I have no one left in my life.

982
01:33:52,833 --> 01:33:53,708
From now on,

983
01:33:54,333 --> 01:33:57,416
I'm going to do everything
to protect my daughter from harm.

984
01:33:58,416 --> 01:33:59,791
I'm even willing to die.

985
01:34:02,500 --> 01:34:04,833
Why did Nim die?
The spirits did it, right?

986
01:34:07,750 --> 01:34:09,166
There's no way to know.

987
01:34:10,041 --> 01:34:11,416
What's that supposed to mean?

988
01:34:14,333 --> 01:34:15,541
Why are you saying such things?

989
01:34:15,625 --> 01:34:18,375
Master, what are we supposed to do now?

990
01:34:19,208 --> 01:34:20,291
Don't worry.

991
01:34:20,958 --> 01:34:24,250
Tomorrow, we will conduct
the ceremony as planned.

992
01:34:33,416 --> 01:34:37,791
DAY OF CEREMONY

993
01:34:56,291 --> 01:34:58,875
-Right here?
-Yeah. Put it right here.

994
01:34:58,958 --> 01:35:02,583
Master Santi,
please tell us about today's ceremony.

995
01:35:03,666 --> 01:35:05,333
The ceremony will be on the 5th floor.

996
01:35:06,583 --> 01:35:08,041
The first thing I have to do is

997
01:35:09,333 --> 01:35:10,750
summon the evil spirits to gather

998
01:35:11,416 --> 01:35:12,416
into Mink's body.

999
01:35:34,041 --> 01:35:34,875
Then,

1000
01:35:35,708 --> 01:35:36,791
I'll expel the spirits

1001
01:35:38,250 --> 01:35:40,791
into the cursed pot.

1002
01:35:41,625 --> 01:35:44,375
And I'll take the pot to the ground floor,

1003
01:35:45,416 --> 01:35:47,666
bury it,
and perform a spellbinding ritual.

1004
01:35:48,250 --> 01:35:50,791
Based on what happened to Nim,

1005
01:35:50,875 --> 01:35:53,791
will it be too risky to let Mink
still be a part of the ceremony?

1006
01:35:54,875 --> 01:35:55,958
Well, yeah.

1007
01:35:57,458 --> 01:35:58,791
But…

1008
01:35:59,541 --> 01:36:01,250
have you noticed the back of Manit's car?

1009
01:36:02,000 --> 01:36:03,916
It has a sticker that says…

1010
01:36:04,875 --> 01:36:06,208
"This car is red."

1011
01:36:06,291 --> 01:36:08,875
THIS CAR IS RED

1012
01:36:10,458 --> 01:36:12,875
What does that have to do
with the ceremony?

1013
01:36:37,500 --> 01:36:39,250
Don't let anyone

1014
01:36:39,333 --> 01:36:41,166
leave the area

1015
01:36:41,250 --> 01:36:43,041
until the ceremony is over.

1016
01:38:14,041 --> 01:38:15,333
Come and eat!

1017
01:39:06,958 --> 01:39:08,958
Come on! Come and get it!

1018
01:39:09,041 --> 01:39:09,916
Come!

1019
01:39:24,958 --> 01:39:26,250
Why did she scream?

1020
01:39:29,916 --> 01:39:30,916
I don't know.

1021
01:40:14,250 --> 01:40:15,458
Noi!

1022
01:40:15,541 --> 01:40:16,708
Noi!

1023
01:40:16,791 --> 01:40:17,791
Noi!

1024
01:40:18,708 --> 01:40:19,541
-Noi.
-How is she?

1025
01:40:19,625 --> 01:40:21,916
-She's just blacked out.
-Take her to rest up.

1026
01:40:22,625 --> 01:40:24,333
Noi!

1027
01:40:25,333 --> 01:40:26,166
Noi!

1028
01:40:27,458 --> 01:40:28,583
How are you, Noi?

1029
01:40:29,250 --> 01:40:30,416
Can you hear me?

1030
01:40:41,375 --> 01:40:43,166
Is there anyone out there?

1031
01:40:45,291 --> 01:40:46,833
Why am I being locked up?

1032
01:40:48,208 --> 01:40:50,666
Mom? Are you outside?

1033
01:40:50,750 --> 01:40:52,750
Please open the door.

1034
01:40:52,833 --> 01:40:54,250
Did the spirit leave already?

1035
01:40:55,583 --> 01:40:56,791
I don't know.

1036
01:40:57,416 --> 01:40:58,791
Pang?

1037
01:40:58,875 --> 01:40:59,958
Mink.

1038
01:41:00,041 --> 01:41:01,875
Pang, open the door for me.

1039
01:41:01,958 --> 01:41:02,958
Mink!

1040
01:41:03,041 --> 01:41:04,708
You're better now, right?

1041
01:41:05,875 --> 01:41:06,958
Open the door.

1042
01:41:07,041 --> 01:41:08,250
She's well now, right?

1043
01:41:08,791 --> 01:41:10,041
Pang, I'm in here.

1044
01:41:10,125 --> 01:41:11,250
Open the door, please.

1045
01:41:11,333 --> 01:41:12,208
I don't know.

1046
01:41:12,291 --> 01:41:14,875
The Master told us not to open the door
if the ceremony isn't over.

1047
01:41:14,958 --> 01:41:17,375
-Please open the door.
-Mink.

1048
01:41:17,875 --> 01:41:21,416
Open the door for me, please.
I'm locked up in here.

1049
01:41:22,125 --> 01:41:23,000
Hold on.

1050
01:41:23,083 --> 01:41:25,333
-Pang, please open the door.
-Mink.

1051
01:41:25,416 --> 01:41:27,375
No one has called to let us know yet.

1052
01:41:27,458 --> 01:41:31,333
Pang. Where are all of you? Pang?

1053
01:41:31,416 --> 01:41:32,291
Mink.

1054
01:41:32,375 --> 01:41:34,166
Pang, open the door.

1055
01:41:48,583 --> 01:41:49,916
Mink, are you okay?

1056
01:41:52,583 --> 01:41:53,500
Mink.

1057
01:42:22,541 --> 01:42:23,458
Pong.

1058
01:42:26,875 --> 01:42:28,458
Open the door. My son is in there.

1059
01:42:28,541 --> 01:42:29,458
-We can't.
-Open it!

